Package be.kdg.simulator.camera

Class CameraMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • be.kdg.simulator.camera.CameraMessage
  • public class CameraMessage
extends java.lang.Object
    Model class that holds information about a camera message. Gets sent to an MQTT queue via QueueMessenger or to console via CommandlineMessenger.
    Author:
    Cédric Goffin
    See Also:
    QueueMessenger, CommandlineMessenger, FileGenerator, RandomGenerator, ImageGenerator
